                        <additions>
                            <list>
                                <item xml:id="a1">
                                    <desc type="Inventory"/>
                                    <locus target="#248"/>
                                    <q xml:lang="gez">
                                        ኍልቈ፡ መጻሕፍት፡ ዘቤተ፡ ክርስቲያን። ፪ትርጓሜ፡ ጰውሎስ። ፩ትርጓሜ፡ ዕብራውያን። ፩ውዳሴ፡ አምላክ፡ ምስለ፡ ዮሐንስ፡ ወንጌል። ፩ገድለ፡ ሐዋርያት። ፩ገድለ፡ ጴጥሮስ። ፩ኦርጋኖን። ፩ትርጓሜ፡ 
                                        ደዊት። ፩መጽሐፈ፡ መድኃኒት፡ ምስለ፡ በአውልት። ፩ድጓ። ፪ዝማሬ። ፩ትርጓሜ፡ ደቂቀ፡ ነቢያት። ፩አፈ፡ ወርቅ። ዮሐንስ፡ ወንጌል፡ ምስለ፡ ቀለምሲስ። ሲኖዶስ። ፩አረጋዊ፡ ጰውሎስ። ፩ዜና፡ 
                                        አይሁድ። ፩ዜና፡ አበው፡ ዘበልዕዎ፡ አናጹት። ወኵሉ፡ ድሙር፡ ፲ወ፱፡ ፩ኪዳን፡ ዘምስለ፡ መዝገበ፡ መልክዕ፡ ወስብሐተ፡ ፍቁር፡ ወሰዓታት፡ ዘመአልት፡ ገድለ፡ ገብረ፡ መንፈስ፡ ቅዱስ። ፩አረቢ።
                                    </q>
                                    <desc>The inventory lists the books belonging to the church: two <title ref="LIT3181Commen">Tǝrgʷāme Ṗāwlos</title>, one <title ref="LIT3171Commen">Tǝrgʷāme ʿƎbrāwǝyān</title>, 
                                        one <title ref="LIT2505Weddas">Wǝddāse ʾAmlāk</title> with the <title ref="LIT1693John">Gospel of John</title>, 
                                        one <title ref="LIT1461Gadlah">Gadla ḥawāryāt</title>, one Gadla Ṗeṭros, one <title ref="LIT1146Argano">ʾArgānona Māryām</title>, 
                                        one <title ref="LIT3182Commen">Tǝrgʷāme Dāwit</title>, one <title ref="LIT1942Mashaf">Maṣḥafa madḫanit</title> with commemorations, 
                                        one <title ref="LIT3178Deggwa">Dǝggʷā</title>, two <title ref="LIT2610Zemmar">Zǝmmāre</title>, one <title ref="LIT3183Commen">Tǝrgʷāme daqiqa nabiyāt</title>, 
                                        one <title ref="LIT3184Afawarq">ʾAfa Warq</title>, <title ref="LIT1693John">Gospel of John</title> with the 
                                        <title ref="LIT3179Revela">Revelation</title>, one <title ref="LIT2317Senodo">Sinodos</title>, one ʾAragāwi Ṗawlos (presumably 
                                        the <title ref="LIT1799Lifeof">Life of Paul the First Hermit</title> ), one <title ref="LIT2598Yosipp">Zenā ʾAyhud</title>, one <title ref="LIT2611Zenaab">Zenā ʾabaw</title>. 
                                        The total amount of the previous books is 19. Additionally, one Kidān with the <title ref="LIT3185Mazgab">Mazgaba malkǝʾ</title>, 
                                        the <title ref="LIT2300Sebhat">Sǝbḥata fǝqur</title> and the <title ref="LIT2231Saatat">Saʿātāt za-maʿālt</title>, 
                                        one <title ref="LIT1451GadlaG">Gadla Gabra Manfas Qǝddus</title>, one in Arabic.</desc>
                                </item>
                                
                                <item xml:id="a2">
                                    <desc type="Inventory"/>
                                    <locus target="#248"/>
                                    <q xml:lang="gez">
                                        ዘሀለወ፡ ለአባ፡ ተስፋ፡ ወንጌል፡ ዮሐንስ፡ ምስለ፡ ቀለምሲስ፡ ፩ደዊት፡ የአባ፡ ስጦት፡ በቄስባይነሶ፡ ፩ድጓ፡ ፩ዝማሬ፡ ምስለ፡ ምዕራፍ፡ ወመዋሥዕት፡ ወቃለ፡ ትምህርት፡ ወውዳሴ፡ ማርያም፡ ፲ወ፬ቅዳሴ፡ 
                                        ወሊጦን፡ ወዘይነግሥ፡ <gap reason="omitted" extent="unknown"/> ፩ዜና፡ ስላሴ።
                                    </q>
                                    <desc>The inventory is partly written in Amharic, in a different hand than that of <ref target="#a1"/>. 
                                        It lists the books belonging to ʾabbā <persName ref="PRS10796Tasfo"/>, i.e. the <title ref="LIT1693John">Gospel of John</title> 
                                        with the <title ref="LIT3179Revela">Revelation</title> and the <title ref="LIT2701Dawit">Dāwit</title>, 
                                        and those belonging to ʾabbā <persName ref="PRS10797Setot"/>,  i.e. one <title ref="LIT3178Deggwa">Dǝggʷā</title>, 
                                        one <title ref="LIT2610Zemmar">Zǝmmāre</title> with the <title ref="LIT3186Meeraf">Mǝʿǝrāf</title>and the <title ref="LIT1990Mawase">Mawāśǝʾǝt</title>, 
                                        the <title ref="LIT3187Qalatem">Qāla tǝmhǝrt</title>, the <title ref="LIT2509Weddas">Wǝddāse Māryām</title>, 
                                        the <title ref="LIT3189Anapho">fourteen Anaphoras</title>, the <title ref="LIT3188Liton">Liṭon</title>, 
                                        the <title ref="LIT2605Zayena">Za-yǝnaggǝś</title>, one <title ref="LIT1300Dersan">Zenā śǝllāse</title>
                                    </desc>
                                </item>
                                
                                <item xml:id="a3">
                                    <desc type="Inventory"/>
                                    <locus target="#248"/>
                                    <q xml:lang="gez">
                                        እምእሉ፡ ዘበጽሐኒ፡ ሊተ፡ ዘማርያም። ትርጓሜ፡ ዕብራውያን። ገድለ፡ ሐዋርያት። ገድለ፡ ጴጥሮስ። መጽሐፈ፡ መድኀኒት። ድጓ። ፪ዝማሬ። አረጋዊ፡ ጰውሎስ። ዜና፡ ሥላሴ። ሰዓታት፡ ዘመዓልት። 
                                        ገድለ፡ ገብረ፡ መንፈስ፡ ቅዱስ። ትርጓሜ፡ ጰውሎስ።
                                    </q>
                                    <desc>The inventory is written in the same hand as that of <ref target="#a2"/>. It lists the books received by the author of the note, 
                                        called <persName ref="PRS10798Zamaryam"/>. 
                                        The books are: the <title ref="LIT3171Commen">Tǝrgʷāme ʿƎbrāwǝyān</title>, the <title ref="LIT1461Gadlah">Gadla ḥawāryāt</title>, the Gadla Ṗeṭros, the <title ref="LIT1942Mashaf">Maṣḥafa madḫanit</title>, 
                                        the <title ref="LIT3178Deggwa">Dǝggʷā</title>, two <title ref="LIT2610Zemmar">Zǝmmāre</title>, one ʾAragāwi Ṗawlos 
                                        (presumably the <title ref="LIT1799Lifeof">Life of Paul the First Hermit</title> ), 
                                        the <title ref="LIT2611Zenaab">Zenā ʾabaw</title>, the <title ref="LIT1300Dersan">Zenā śǝllāse</title>, the 
                                        <title ref="LIT2231Saatat">Saʿātāt za-maʿālt</title>, the <title ref="LIT1451GadlaG">Gadla Gabra Manfas Qǝddus</title>, 
                                        <title ref="LIT3181Commen">Tǝrgʷāme Ṗāwlos</title>.</desc>
                                </item>
                                
                            </list>
